{"tid":1561333,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[人山人海] 大埔、沙田、油塘多區居民晚上接力大合唱","createTime":"2019-09-11T14:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T14:32:24.000Z","uid":224066,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c90f268f49e71ef2fa87f9281011605e03f98257","tid":1561333,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:25:11.000Z","msg":"《逃犯條例》修訂風波至今，社會上出現接連發生示威衝突，除了集會遊行，有市民以不同方式表達反對修例的聲音，包括築人鏈、默站活動等，而最近一首歌曲《願榮光歸香港》響徹不同場合，繼周一及周二於太古城、將軍澳、大埔、黃大仙等，今晚一連第三晚有市民在沙田、大埔、荃灣、油塘、香港仔等各區商場高唱歌曲，以歌聲表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3273635/org/811d1f9214350260ea5af577365a3bfe.jpg/adbCt_mhK688CNYXtUQOxGzwcGR72Fm-blE1825RNfM?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3273635%2Forg%2F811d1f9214350260ea5af577365a3bfe.jpg%2FadbCt_mhK688CNYXtUQOxGzwcGR72Fm-blE1825RNfM%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=fdd590d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3273638/org/2c1753a3b78b239b82d21acb49488c0a.jpg/tdUEeuZG2Yr6QeaX9xnrrhKfIa5sDgDkf0HmN39B5jc?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3273638%2Forg%2F2c1753a3b78b239b82d21acb49488c0a.jpg%2FtdUEeuZG2Yr6QeaX9xnrrhKfIa5sDgDkf0HmN39B5jc%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=69cb6ddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3273574/org/4bbfbd290362febd8ae10e813f4ad8c4.jpg/BJY0jc1NTpSSiLt345Ge9VBgROUUKzXl4G2oLuBtqC4?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3273574%2Forg%2F4bbfbd290362febd8ae10e813f4ad8c4.jpg%2FBJY0jc1NTpSSiLt345Ge9VBgROUUKzXl4G2oLuBtqC4%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=33d7b6e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3273543/org/3403da5108d3e5580aef2e5a08173ba4.jpg/MFfizpvBDX-TeWqn_9z2GnXiXEtHMRYZuTr5bLk6-Ww?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2